  <?dbhtml filename="xcmiscproto.html"?>

  <title>xcmiscproto-&xcmiscproto-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      This extension defines a protocol that provides Xlib two ways to query the
      server for available resource IDs.
    </para>

